  "title": "Admin Assistant | Claims",
  "description": "<p>HMI OneCare is hiring!</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Data entry; To do insurance claims for outpatient visit (Healthcare schemes: e.g: MHC, FHN)</li><li>Collecting accurate information and documents to proceed with a claim</li><li>To have timely follow-up with healthcare providers and business partners for claims related matters/ documentations</li><li>Ensuring claim settlement is concluded within the agreed turnaround time</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Candidate must possess at least \"O\"/\"N\" Level/ Relevant Professional Certificates</li><li><strong>Rotating between Office Hours and Shift hours (8am-4pm; 5pm-10pm), Weekend and Public holiday</strong></li><li>Computer Savvy and meticulous with work</li></ul><p><strong>Working Location: </strong>IMM Building</p>",
