    "description": "<p>Established in 2013 by a group of experienced doctors, and a part of HMI Medical, HMI OneCare Clinic (formerly known as OneCare Medical) is Singapore’s leading General Practitioner (GP) clinic chain that aims to deliver accessible healthcare to all.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>With more than 35 clinic locations islandwide, we offer a comprehensive range of primary healthcare services, such as acute consultations, minor procedures, statutory check-ups, health screening, vaccinations, and many more.</p>\n<p>Join our passionate team of over 200 dedicated professionals, including clinic assistants, nurses, doctors, administrative staff and support personnel where our core values of Compassion, Competence and Collaboration drive our commitment to deliver more, with care.</p>",
